# Docs last updated for version

v1.12.0

## How to use this file

When updating docs next time, run:

```bash
# Get all changes since docs were last updated
git log v1.12.0..HEAD --oneline
```

Then update this file to the new version after the docs PR is merged.

## What was covered in this update

- Remote state client for distributed GHA matrix execution (`--remote-state`, `--backend-url`)
- `orun status` new flags: `--watch`, `--interval`, `--remote-state`, `--backend-url`
- `orun logs` new flags: `--failed`, `--raw`, `--remote-state`, `--backend-url`
- `intent.yaml` schema: `execution.state.{mode,backendUrl}`
- New env vars: `ORUN_REMOTE_STATE`, `ORUN_BACKEND_URL`, `ORUN_TOKEN`
- Step env vars: `ORUN_PLAN_ID`, `ORUN_JOB_ID`, `ORUN_JOB_RUN_ID`
- New example: distributed execution with remote state (GHA matrix)
- Fix: `--changed` exits 0 when no components are affected (v1.11.0)
